data.revised_prompt: A stylish, dark purple sports car in the style of a Maserati GranTurismo is driving through a tunnel, which enhances the car's sleek lines and vibrant hue. This scene is fashioned in a retrowave theme, which adds a nostalgic, futuristic feel to the image. The time of day is early morning, with the first light of dawn just beginning to flood into the mouth of the tunnel. Embodying the mood of happiness, the car takes up less than 50% of the image, allowing the city vista spread out around it and in the distance to be part of the overall composition.  Blazing neon lights juxtapose against centuries-old architecture, with towering buildings piercing the skyline.
